var book = {
	"name": "Zechariah",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the eighth month of the second year of Darius,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22880A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22880A\"></sup> the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to the prophet Zechariah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22880B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22880B\"></sup> son of Berekiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22880C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22880C\"></sup> the son of Iddo:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22880D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22880D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was very angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22881E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22881E\"></sup> with your ancestors.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore tell the people: This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘Return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22882F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22882F\"></sup> to me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, ‘and I will return to you,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22882G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22882G\"></sup> says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do not be like your ancestors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22883H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22883H\"></sup> to whom the earlier prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22883I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22883I\"></sup> proclaimed: This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘Turn from your evil ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22883J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22883J\"></sup> and your evil practices.’ But they would not listen or pay attention to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22883K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22883K\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22883L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22883L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Where are your ancestors now? And the prophets, do they live forever?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But did not my words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22885M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22885M\"></sup> and my decrees, which I commanded my servants the prophets, overtake your ancestors?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22885N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22885N\"></sup>“Then they repented and said, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has done to us what our ways and practices deserve,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22885O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22885O\"></sup> just as he determined to do.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22885P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22885P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On the twenty-fourth day of the eleventh month, the month of Shebat, in the second year of Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to the prophet Zechariah son of Berekiah, the son of Iddo.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22886Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22886Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>During the night I had a vision, and there before me was a man mounted on a red<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22887R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22887R\"></sup> horse. He was standing among the myrtle trees in a ravine. Behind him were red, brown and white horses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22887S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22887S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I asked, “What are these, my lord?”The angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22888T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22888T\"></sup> who was talking with me answered, “I will show you what they are.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22888U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22888U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the man standing among the myrtle trees explained, “They are the ones the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent to go throughout the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22889V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22889V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they reported to the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22890W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22890W\"></sup> who was standing among the myrtle trees, “We have gone throughout the earth and found the whole world at rest and in peace.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22890X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22890X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, how long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22891Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22891Y\"></sup> will you withhold mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22891Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22891Z\"></sup> from Jerusalem and from the towns of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22891AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22891AA\"></sup> which you have been angry with these seventy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22891AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22891AB\"></sup> years?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22892AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22892AC\"></sup> kind and comforting words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22892AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22892AD\"></sup> to the angel who talked with me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22892AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22892AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the angel who was speaking to me said, “Proclaim this word: This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘I am very jealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22893AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22893AF\"></sup> for Jerusalem and Zion,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and I am very angry with the nations that feel secure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22894AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22894AG\"></sup> I was only a little angry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22894AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22894AH\"></sup> but they went too far with the punishment.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22894AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22894AI\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘I will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22895AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22895AJ\"></sup> to Jerusalem with mercy, and there my house will be rebuilt. And the measuring line<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22895AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22895AK\"></sup> will be stretched out over Jerusalem,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22895AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22895AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Proclaim further: This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘My towns will again overflow with prosperity, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will again comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22896AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22896AM\"></sup> Zion and choose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22896AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22896AN\"></sup> Jerusalem.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22896AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22896AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then I looked up, and there before me were four horns.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I asked the angel who was speaking to me, “What are these?”He answered me, “These are the horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22898AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22898AP\"></sup> that scattered Judah, Israel and Jerusalem.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me four craftsmen.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I asked, “What are these coming to do?”He answered, “These are the horns that scattered Judah so that no one could raise their head, but the craftsmen have come to terrify them and throw down these horns of the nations who lifted up their horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22900AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22900AQ\"></sup> against the land of Judah to scatter its people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22900AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22900AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then I looked up, and there before me was a man with a measuring line in his hand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I asked, “Where are you going?”He answered me, “To measure Jerusalem, to find out how wide and how long it is.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22902A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22902A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>While the angel who was speaking to me was leaving, another angel came to meet him",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and said to him: “Run, tell that young man, ‘Jerusalem will be a city without walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22904B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22904B\"></sup> because of the great number<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22904C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22904C\"></sup> of people and animals in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22904D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22904D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I myself will be a wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22905E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22905E\"></sup> of fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22905F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22905F\"></sup> around it,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and I will be its glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22905G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22905G\"></sup> within.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22905H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Come! Come! Flee from the land of the north,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for I have scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22906I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22906I\"></sup> you to the four winds of heaven,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22906J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22906J\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22906K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22906K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Come, Zion! Escape,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22907L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22907L\"></sup> you who live in Daughter Babylon!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22907M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22907M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “After the Glorious One has sent me against the nations that have plundered you—for whoever touches you touches the apple of his eye<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22908N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22908N\"></sup>—",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will surely raise my hand against them so that their slaves will plunder them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22909O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22909O\"></sup> Then you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sent me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22909P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22909P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Shout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22910Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22910Q\"></sup> and be glad, Daughter Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22910R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22910R\"></sup> For I am coming,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22910S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22910S\"></sup> and I will live among you,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22910T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22910T\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22910U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22910U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Many nations will be joined with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in that day and will become my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22911V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22911V\"></sup> I will live among you and you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sent me to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22911W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22911W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will inherit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22912X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22912X\"></sup> Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22912Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22912Y\"></sup> as his portion in the holy land and will again choose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22912Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22912Z\"></sup> Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Be still<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22913AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22913AA\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all mankind, because he has roused himself from his holy dwelling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22913AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22913AB\"></sup>”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then he showed me Joshua<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22914A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22914A\"></sup> the high priest standing before the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22914B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22914B\"></sup> standing at his right side to accuse him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rebuke you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22915C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22915C\"></sup> Satan! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who has chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22915D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22915D\"></sup> Jerusalem, rebuke you! Is not this man a burning stick<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22915E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22915E\"></sup> snatched from the fire?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22915F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22915F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now Joshua was dressed in filthy clothes as he stood before the angel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The angel said to those who were standing before him, “Take off his filthy clothes.”Then he said to Joshua, “See, I have taken away your sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22917G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22917G\"></sup> and I will put fine garments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22917H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22917H\"></sup> on you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I said, “Put a clean turban<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22918I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22918I\"></sup> on his head.” So they put a clean turban on his head and clothed him, while the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> stood by.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave this charge to Joshua:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘If you will walk in obedience to me and keep my requirements,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22920J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22920J\"></sup> then you will govern my house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22920K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22920K\"></sup> and have charge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22920L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22920L\"></sup> of my courts, and I will give you a place among these standing here.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22920M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22920M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘Listen, High Priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22921N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22921N\"></sup> Joshua, you and your associates seated before you, who are men symbolic<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22921O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22921O\"></sup> of things to come: I am going to bring my servant, the Branch.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22921P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22921P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>See, the stone I have set in front of Joshua!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22922Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22922Q\"></sup> There are seven eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22922R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22922R\"></sup> on that one stone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22922S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22922S\"></sup> and I will engrave an inscription on it,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, ‘and I will remove the sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22922T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22922T\"></sup> of this land in a single day.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘In that day each of you will invite your neighbor to sit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22923U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22923U\"></sup> under your vine and fig tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22923V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22923V\"></sup>’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Then the angel who talked with me returned and woke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22924A\"></sup> me up, like someone awakened from sleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22924B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He asked me, “What do you see?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22925C\"></sup>I answered, “I see a solid gold lampstand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22925D\"></sup> with a bowl at the top and seven lamps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22925E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22925E\"></sup> on it, with seven channels to the lamps.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Also there are two olive trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22926F\"></sup> by it, one on the right of the bowl and the other on its left.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I asked the angel who talked with me, “What are these, my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He answered, “Do you not know what these are?”“No, my lord,” I replied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22928G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22928G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So he said to me, “This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Zerubbabel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22929H\"></sup> ‘Not<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22929I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22929I\"></sup> by might nor by power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22929J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22929J\"></sup> but by my Spirit,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22929K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22929K\"></sup> says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“What are you, mighty mountain? Before Zerubbabel you will become level ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22930L\"></sup> Then he will bring out the capstone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22930M\"></sup> to shouts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22930N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22930N\"></sup> of ‘God bless it! God bless it!’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The hands of Zerubbabel have laid the foundation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22932O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22932O\"></sup> of this temple; his hands will also complete it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22932P\"></sup> Then you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sent me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22932Q\"></sup> to you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Who dares despise the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22933R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22933R\"></sup> of small things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22933S\"></sup> since the seven eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22933T\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that range throughout the earth will rejoice when they see the chosen capstone in the hand of Zerubbabel?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22933U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I asked the angel, “What are these two olive trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22934V\"></sup> on the right and the left of the lampstand?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Again I asked him, “What are these two olive branches beside the two gold pipes that pour out golden oil?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He replied, “Do you not know what these are?”“No, my lord,” I said.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So he said, “These are the two who are anointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22937W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22937W\"></sup> to serve the Lord of all the earth.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>I looked again, and there before me was a flying scroll.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22938A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22938A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He asked me, “What do you see?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22939B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22939B\"></sup>I answered, “I see a flying scroll, twenty cubits long and ten cubits wide.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said to me, “This is the curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22940C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22940C\"></sup> that is going out over the whole land; for according to what it says on one side, every thief<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22940D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22940D\"></sup> will be banished, and according to what it says on the other, everyone who swears falsely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22940E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22940E\"></sup> will be banished.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty declares, ‘I will send it out, and it will enter the house of the thief and the house of anyone who swears falsely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22941F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22941F\"></sup> by my name. It will remain in that house and destroy it completely, both its timbers and its stones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22941G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22941G\"></sup>’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel who was speaking to me came forward and said to me, “Look up and see what is appearing.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I asked, “What is it?”He replied, “It is a basket.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22943H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22943H\"></sup>” And he added, “This is the iniquity of the people throughout the land.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the cover of lead was raised, and there in the basket sat a woman!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said, “This is wickedness,” and he pushed her back into the basket and pushed its lead cover down on it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22945I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22945I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I looked up—and there before me were two women, with the wind in their wings! They had wings like those of a stork,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22946J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22946J\"></sup> and they lifted up the basket between heaven and earth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Where are they taking the basket?” I asked the angel who was speaking to me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He replied, “To the country of Babylonia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22948K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22948K\"></sup> to build a house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22948L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22948L\"></sup> for it. When the house is ready, the basket will be set there in its place.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22948M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22948M\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>I looked up again, and there before me were four chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22949A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22949A\"></sup> coming out from between two mountains—mountains of bronze.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The first chariot had red horses, the second black,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22950B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22950B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the third white,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22951C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22951C\"></sup> and the fourth dappled—all of them powerful.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I asked the angel who was speaking to me, “What are these, my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The angel answered me, “These are the four spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22953D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22953D\"></sup> of heaven, going out from standing in the presence of the Lord of the whole world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22953E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22953E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The one with the black horses is going toward the north country, the one with the white horses toward the west, and the one with the dappled horses toward the south.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the powerful horses went out, they were straining to go throughout the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22955F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22955F\"></sup> And he said, “Go throughout the earth!” So they went throughout the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he called to me, “Look, those going toward the north country have given my Spirit rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22956G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22956G\"></sup> in the land of the north.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22956H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22956H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Take silver and gold from the exiles Heldai, Tobijah and Jedaiah, who have arrived from Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22958I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22958I\"></sup> Go the same day to the house of Josiah son of Zephaniah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Take the silver and gold and make a crown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22959J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22959J\"></sup> and set it on the head of the high priest, Joshua<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22959K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22959K\"></sup> son of Jozadak.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22959L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22959L\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Tell him this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘Here is the man whose name is the Branch,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22960M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22960M\"></sup> and he will branch out from his place and build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22960N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22960N\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It is he who will build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will be clothed with majesty and will sit and rule on his throne. And he will be a priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22961O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22961O\"></sup> on his throne. And there will be harmony between the two.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The crown will be given to Heldai, Tobijah, Jedaiah and Hen son of Zephaniah as a memorial<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22962P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22962P\"></sup> in the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Those who are far away will come and help to build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22963Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22963Q\"></sup> and you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sent me to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22963R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22963R\"></sup> This will happen if you diligently obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22963S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22963S\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>In the fourth year of King Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22964A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22964A\"></sup> on the fourth day of the ninth month, the month of Kislev.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22964B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22964B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The people of Bethel had sent Sharezer and Regem-Melek, together with their men, to entreat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22965C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22965C\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22965D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22965D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>by asking the priests of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty and the prophets, “Should I mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22966E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22966E\"></sup> and fast in the fifth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22966F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22966F\"></sup> month, as I have done for so many years?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty came to me:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Ask all the people of the land and the priests, ‘When you fasted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22968G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22968G\"></sup> and mourned in the fifth and seventh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22968H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22968H\"></sup> months for the past seventy years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22968I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22968I\"></sup> was it really for me that you fasted?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when you were eating and drinking, were you not just feasting for yourselves?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22969J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22969J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Are these not the words the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> proclaimed through the earlier prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22970K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22970K\"></sup> when Jerusalem and its surrounding towns were at rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22970L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22970L\"></sup> and prosperous, and the Negev and the western foothills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22970M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22970M\"></sup> were settled?’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22970N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22970N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came again to Zechariah:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty said: ‘Administer true justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22972O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22972O\"></sup> show mercy and compassion to one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22972P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22972P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not oppress the widow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22973Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22973Q\"></sup> or the fatherless, the foreigner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22973R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22973R\"></sup> or the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22973S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22973S\"></sup> Do not plot evil against each other.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22973T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22973T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But they refused to pay attention; stubbornly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22974U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22974U\"></sup> they turned their backs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22974V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22974V\"></sup> and covered their ears.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22974W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22974W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They made their hearts as hard as flint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22975X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22975X\"></sup> and would not listen to the law or to the words that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty had sent by his Spirit through the earlier prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22975Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22975Y\"></sup> So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty was very angry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22975Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22975Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘When I called, they did not listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22976AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22976AA\"></sup> so when they called, I would not listen,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22976AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22976AB\"></sup> says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22976AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22976AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘I scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22977AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22977AD\"></sup> them with a whirlwind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22977AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22977AE\"></sup> among all the nations, where they were strangers. The land they left behind them was so desolate that no one traveled through it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22977AF\"></sup> This is how they made the pleasant land desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22977AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22977AG\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty came to me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “I am very jealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22979A\"></sup> for Zion; I am burning with jealousy for her.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “I will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980B\"></sup> to Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980C\"></sup> and dwell in Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980D\"></sup> Then Jerusalem will be called the Faithful City,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980E\"></sup> and the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980F\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will be called the Holy Mountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22980G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22980G\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “Once again men and women of ripe old age will sit in the streets of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22981H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22981H\"></sup> each of them with cane in hand because of their age.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The city streets will be filled with boys and girls playing there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22982I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22982I\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “It may seem marvelous to the remnant of this people at that time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22983J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22983J\"></sup> but will it seem marvelous to me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22983K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22983K\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “I will save my people from the countries of the east and the west.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22984L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22984L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will bring them back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22985M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22985M\"></sup> to live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22985N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22985N\"></sup> in Jerusalem; they will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22985O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22985O\"></sup> and I will be faithful and righteous to them as their God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22985P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22985P\"></sup>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “Now hear these words, ‘Let your hands be strong<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22986Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22986Q\"></sup> so that the temple may be built.’ This is also what the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22986R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22986R\"></sup> said who were present when the foundation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22986S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22986S\"></sup> was laid for the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Before that time there were no wages<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22987T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22987T\"></sup> for people or hire for animals. No one could go about their business safely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22987U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22987U\"></sup> because of their enemies, since I had turned everyone against their neighbor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now I will not deal with the remnant of this people as I did in the past,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22988V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22988V\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“The seed will grow well, the vine will yield its fruit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22989W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22989W\"></sup> the ground will produce its crops,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22989X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22989X\"></sup> and the heavens will drop their dew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22989Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22989Y\"></sup> I will give all these things as an inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22989Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22989Z\"></sup> to the remnant of this people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22989AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22989AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Just as you, Judah and Israel, have been a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22990AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22990AB\"></sup> among the nations, so I will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22990AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22990AC\"></sup> you, and you will be a blessing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22990AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22990AD\"></sup> Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22990AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22990AE\"></sup> but let your hands be strong.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22990AF\"></sup>”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “Just as I had determined to bring disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22991AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22991AG\"></sup> on you and showed no pity when your ancestors angered me,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“so now I have determined to do good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22992AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22992AH\"></sup> again to Jerusalem and Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22992AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22992AI\"></sup> Do not be afraid.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>These are the things you are to do: Speak the truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22993AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22993AJ\"></sup> to each other, and render true and sound judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22993AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22993AK\"></sup> in your courts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22993AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22993AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>do not plot evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22994AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22994AM\"></sup> against each other, and do not love to swear falsely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22994AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22994AN\"></sup> I hate all this,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty came to me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “The fasts of the fourth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AO\"></sup> fifth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AP\"></sup> seventh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AQ\"></sup> and tenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AR\"></sup> months will become joyful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AS\"></sup> and glad occasions and happy festivals for Judah. Therefore love truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22996AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22996AT\"></sup> and peace.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “Many peoples and the inhabitants of many cities will yet come,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and the inhabitants of one city will go to another and say, ‘Let us go at once to entreat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22998AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22998AU\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22998AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22998AV\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty. I myself am going.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And many peoples and powerful nations will come to Jerusalem to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty and to entreat him.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22999AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22999AW\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “In those days ten people from all languages and nations will take firm hold of one Jew by the hem of his robe and say, ‘Let us go with you, because we have heard that God is with you.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23000AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23000AX\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>A prophecy:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23001A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23001A\"></sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is against the land of Hadrakand will come to rest on Damascus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23001B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23001B\"></sup>—for the eyes of all people and all the tribes of Israelare on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and on Hamath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23002C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23002C\"></sup> too, which borders on it,and on Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23002D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23002D\"></sup> and Sidon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23002E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23002E\"></sup> though they are very skillful.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Tyre has built herself a stronghold;she has heaped up silver like dust,and gold like the dirt of the streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23003F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23003F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the Lord will take away her possessionsand destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23004G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23004G\"></sup> her power on the sea,and she will be consumed by fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23004H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23004H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Ashkelon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23005I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23005I\"></sup> will see it and fear;Gaza will writhe in agony,and Ekron too, for her hope will wither.Gaza will lose her kingand Ashkelon will be deserted.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A mongrel people will occupy Ashdod,and I will put an end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23006J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23006J\"></sup> to the pride of the Philistines.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will take the blood from their mouths,the forbidden food from between their teeth.Those who are left will belong to our God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23007K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23007K\"></sup>and become a clan in Judah,and Ekron will be like the Jebusites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23007L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23007L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I will encamp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23008M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23008M\"></sup> at my templeto guard it against marauding forces.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23008N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23008N\"></sup>Never again will an oppressor overrun my people,for now I am keeping watch.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23008O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23008O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Rejoice greatly, Daughter Zion!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009P\"></sup>Shout,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009Q\"></sup> Daughter Jerusalem!See, your king comes to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009R\"></sup>righteous and victorious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009S\"></sup>lowly and riding on a donkey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009T\"></sup>on a colt, the foal of a donkey.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23009U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23009U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will take away the chariots from Ephraimand the warhorses from Jerusalem,and the battle bow will be broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23010V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23010V\"></sup>He will proclaim peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23010W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23010W\"></sup> to the nations.His rule will extend from sea to seaand from the River to the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23010X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23010X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for you, because of the blood of my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23011Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23011Y\"></sup> with you,I will free your prisoners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23011Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23011Z\"></sup> from the waterless pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23011AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23011AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Return to your fortress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23012AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23012AB\"></sup> you prisoners of hope;even now I announce that I will restore twice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23012AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23012AC\"></sup> as much to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bend Judah as I bend my bow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23013AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23013AD\"></sup>and fill it with Ephraim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23013AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23013AE\"></sup>I will rouse your sons, Zion,against your sons, Greece,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23013AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23013AF\"></sup>and make you like a warrior’s sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23013AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23013AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will appear over them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23014AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23014AH\"></sup>his arrow will flash like lightning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23014AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23014AI\"></sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will sound the trumpet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23014AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23014AJ\"></sup>he will march in the storms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23014AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23014AK\"></sup> of the south,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will shield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23015AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23015AL\"></sup> them.They will destroyand overcome with slingstones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23015AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23015AM\"></sup>They will drink and roar as with wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23015AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23015AN\"></sup>they will be full like a bowl<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23015AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23015AO\"></sup>used for sprinkling the corners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23015AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23015AP\"></sup> of the altar.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God will save his people on that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23016AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23016AQ\"></sup>as a shepherd saves his flock.They will sparkle in his landlike jewels in a crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23016AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23016AR\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>How attractive and beautiful they will be!Grain will make the young men thrive,and new wine the young women."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Ask the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for rain in the springtime;it is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who sends the thunderstorms.He gives showers of rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23018A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23018A\"></sup> to all people,and plants of the field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23018B\"></sup> to everyone.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23019C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23019C\"></sup> speak deceitfully,diviners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23019D\"></sup> see visions that lie;they tell dreams<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23019E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23019E\"></sup> that are false,they give comfort in vain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23019F\"></sup>Therefore the people wander like sheepoppressed for lack of a shepherd.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23019G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“My anger burns against the shepherds,and I will punish the leaders;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23020H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23020H\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will carefor his flock, the people of Judah,and make them like a proud horse in battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23020I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23020I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>From Judah will come the cornerstone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23021J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23021J\"></sup>from him the tent peg,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23021K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23021K\"></sup>from him the battle bow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23021L\"></sup>from him every ruler.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Together they will be like warriors in battletrampling their enemy into the mud of the streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23022M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23022M\"></sup>They will fight because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with them,and they will put the enemy horsemen to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23022N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23022N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I will strengthen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23023O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23023O\"></sup> Judahand save the tribes of Joseph.I will restore thembecause I have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23023P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23023P\"></sup> on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23023Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23023Q\"></sup>They will be as thoughI had not rejected them,for I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their Godand I will answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23023R\"></sup> them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The Ephraimites will become like warriors,and their hearts will be glad as with wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23024S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23024S\"></sup>Their children will see it and be joyful;their hearts will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23024T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23024T\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will signal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23025U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23025U\"></sup> for themand gather them in.Surely I will redeem them;they will be as numerous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23025V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23025V\"></sup> as before.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Though I scatter them among the peoples,yet in distant lands they will remember me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23026W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23026W\"></sup>They and their children will survive,and they will return.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will bring them back from Egyptand gather them from Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23027X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23027X\"></sup>I will bring them to Gilead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23027Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23027Y\"></sup> and Lebanon,and there will not be room<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23027Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23027Z\"></sup> enough for them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They will pass through the sea of trouble;the surging sea will be subduedand all the depths of the Nile will dry up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23028AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23028AA\"></sup>Assyria’s pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23028AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23028AB\"></sup> will be brought downand Egypt’s scepter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23028AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23028AC\"></sup> will pass away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23028AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23028AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will strengthen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23029AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23029AE\"></sup> them in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and in his name they will live securely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23029AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23029AF\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Open your doors, Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23030A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23030A\"></sup>so that fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23030B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23030B\"></sup> may devour your cedars!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wail, you juniper, for the cedar has fallen;the stately trees are ruined!Wail, oaks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23031C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23031C\"></sup> of Bashan;the dense forest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23031D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23031D\"></sup> has been cut down!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23031E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23031E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Listen to the wail of the shepherds;their rich pastures are destroyed!Listen to the roar of the lions;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23032F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23032F\"></sup>the lush thicket of the Jordan is ruined!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23032G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23032G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God says: “Shepherd the flock marked for slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23033H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23033H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Their buyers slaughter them and go unpunished. Those who sell them say, ‘Praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I am rich!’ Their own shepherds do not spare them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23034I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23034I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I will no longer have pity on the people of the land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “I will give everyone into the hands of their neighbors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23035J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23035J\"></sup> and their king. They will devastate the land, and I will not rescue anyone from their hands.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23035K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23035K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I shepherded the flock marked for slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23036L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23036L\"></sup> particularly the oppressed of the flock. Then I took two staffs and called one Favor and the other Union, and I shepherded the flock.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In one month I got rid of the three shepherds.The flock detested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23037M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23037M\"></sup> me, and I grew weary of them",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and said, “I will not be your shepherd. Let the dying die, and the perishing perish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23038N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23038N\"></sup> Let those who are left eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23038O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23038O\"></sup> one another’s flesh.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I took my staff called Favor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23039P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23039P\"></sup> and broke it, revoking<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23039Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23039Q\"></sup> the covenant I had made with all the nations.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It was revoked on that day, and so the oppressed of the flock who were watching me knew it was the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I told them, “If you think it best, give me my pay; but if not, keep it.” So they paid me thirty pieces of silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23041R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23041R\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Throw it to the potter”—the handsome price at which they valued me! So I took the thirty pieces of silver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23042S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23042S\"></sup> and threw them to the potter at the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23042T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23042T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I broke my second staff called Union, breaking the family bond between Judah and Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take again the equipment of a foolish shepherd.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For I am going to raise up a shepherd over the land who will not care for the lost, or seek the young, or heal the injured, or feed the healthy, but will eat the meat of the choice sheep, tearing off their hooves.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Woe to the worthless shepherd,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23046U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23046U\"></sup>who deserts the flock!May the sword strike his arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23046V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23046V\"></sup> and his right eye!May his arm be completely withered,his right eye totally blinded!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23046W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23046W\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>A prophecy:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23047A\"></sup> The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Israel.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who stretches out the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23047B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23047B\"></sup> who lays the foundation of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23047C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23047C\"></sup> and who forms the human spirit within a person,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23047D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23047D\"></sup> declares:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I am going to make Jerusalem a cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23048E\"></sup> that sends all the surrounding peoples reeling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23048F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23048F\"></sup> Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23048G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23048G\"></sup> will be besieged as well as Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On that day, when all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23049H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23049H\"></sup> of the earth are gathered against her, I will make Jerusalem an immovable rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23049I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23049I\"></sup> for all the nations. All who try to move it will injure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23049J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23049J\"></sup> themselves.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On that day I will strike every horse with panic and its rider with madness,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “I will keep a watchful eye over Judah, but I will blind all the horses of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23050K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23050K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the clans of Judah will say in their hearts, ‘The people of Jerusalem are strong,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23051L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23051L\"></sup> because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is their God.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“On that day I will make the clans of Judah like a firepot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23052M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23052M\"></sup> in a woodpile, like a flaming torch among sheaves. They will consume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23052N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23052N\"></sup> all the surrounding peoples right and left, but Jerusalem will remain intact<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23052O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23052O\"></sup> in her place.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will save the dwellings of Judah first, so that the honor of the house of David and of Jerusalem’s inhabitants may not be greater than that of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23053P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23053P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will shield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23054Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23054Q\"></sup> those who live in Jerusalem, so that the feeblest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23054R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23054R\"></sup> among them will be like David, and the house of David will be like God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23054S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23054S\"></sup> like the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> going before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23054T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23054T\"></sup> them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>On that day I will set out to destroy all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23055U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23055U\"></sup> that attack Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23055V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23055V\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“And I will pour out on the house of David and the inhabitants of Jerusalem a spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23056W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23056W\"></sup> of grace and supplication.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23056X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23056X\"></sup> They will look on me, the one they have pierced,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23056Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23056Y\"></sup> and they will mourn for him as one mourns for an only child,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23056Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23056Z\"></sup> and grieve bitterly for him as one grieves for a firstborn son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23056AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23056AA\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>On that day the weeping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23057AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23057AB\"></sup> in Jerusalem will be as great as the weeping of Hadad Rimmon in the plain of Megiddo.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23057AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23057AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The land will mourn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23058AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23058AD\"></sup> each clan by itself, with their wives by themselves: the clan of the house of David and their wives, the clan of the house of Nathan and their wives,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>the clan of the house of Levi and their wives, the clan of Shimei and their wives,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and all the rest of the clans and their wives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23060AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23060AE\"></sup>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>“On that day a fountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23061A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23061A\"></sup> will be opened to the house of David and the inhabitants of Jerusalem, to cleanse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23061B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23061B\"></sup> them from sin and impurity.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“On that day, I will banish the names of the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23062C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23062C\"></sup> from the land, and they will be remembered no more,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23062D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23062D\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty. “I will remove both the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23062E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23062E\"></sup> and the spirit of impurity from the land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And if anyone still prophesies, their father and mother, to whom they were born, will say to them, ‘You must die, because you have told lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23063F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23063F\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s name.’ Then their own parents will stab the one who prophesies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23063G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23063G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“On that day every prophet will be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23064H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23064H\"></sup> of their prophetic vision. They will not put on a prophet’s garment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23064I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23064I\"></sup> of hair<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23064J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23064J\"></sup> in order to deceive.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23064K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23064K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Each will say, ‘I am not a prophet. I am a farmer; the land has been my livelihood since my youth.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23065L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23065L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If someone asks, ‘What are these wounds on your body?’ they will answer, ‘The wounds I was given at the house of my friends.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Awake, sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23067M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23067M\"></sup> against my shepherd,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23067N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23067N\"></sup>against the man who is close to me!”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.“Strike the shepherd,and the sheep will be scattered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23067O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23067O\"></sup>and I will turn my hand against the little ones.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the whole land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“two-thirds will be struck down and perish;yet one-third will be left in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23068P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23068P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This third I will put into the fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069Q\"></sup>I will refine them like silver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069R\"></sup>and test them like gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069S\"></sup>They will call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069T\"></sup> on my name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069U\"></sup>and I will answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069V\"></sup> them;I will say, ‘They are my people,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069W\"></sup>and they will say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23069X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23069X\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>A day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23070A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23070A\"></sup> is coming, Jerusalem, when your possessions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23070B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23070B\"></sup> will be plundered and divided up within your very walls.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will gather all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23071C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23071C\"></sup> to Jerusalem to fight against it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23071D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23071D\"></sup> the city will be captured, the houses ransacked, and the women raped.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23071E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23071E\"></sup> Half of the city will go into exile, but the rest of the people will not be taken from the city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23071F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23071F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go out and fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23072G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23072G\"></sup> against those nations, as he fights on a day of battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23072H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23072H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On that day his feet will stand on the Mount of Olives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23073I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23073I\"></sup> east of Jerusalem, and the Mount of Olives will be split<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23073J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23073J\"></sup> in two from east to west, forming a great valley, with half of the mountain moving north and half moving south.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You will flee by my mountain valley, for it will extend to Azel. You will flee as you fled from the earthquake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23074K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23074K\"></sup> in the days of Uzziah king of Judah. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God will come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23074L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23074L\"></sup> and all the holy ones with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23074M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23074M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On that day there will be neither sunlight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23075N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23075N\"></sup> nor cold, frosty darkness.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It will be a unique<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23076O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23076O\"></sup> day—a day known only to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—with no distinction between day and night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23076P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23076P\"></sup> When evening comes, there will be light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23076Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23076Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On that day living water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23077R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23077R\"></sup> will flow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23077S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23077S\"></sup> out from Jerusalem, half of it east<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23077T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23077T\"></sup> to the Dead Sea and half of it west to the Mediterranean Sea, in summer and in winter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23077U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23077U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23078V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23078V\"></sup> over the whole earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23078W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23078W\"></sup> On that day there will be one <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and his name the only name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23078X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23078X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The whole land, from Geba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079Y\"></sup> to Rimmon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079Z\"></sup> south of Jerusalem, will become like the Arabah. But Jerusalem will be raised up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079AA\"></sup> high from the Benjamin Gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079AB\"></sup> to the site of the First Gate, to the Corner Gate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079AC\"></sup> and from the Tower of Hananel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079AD\"></sup> to the royal winepresses, and will remain in its place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23079AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23079AE\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It will be inhabited;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23080AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23080AF\"></sup> never again will it be destroyed. Jerusalem will be secure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23080AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23080AG\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is the plague with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23081AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23081AH\"></sup> all the nations that fought against Jerusalem: Their flesh will rot while they are still standing on their feet, their eyes will rot in their sockets, and their tongues will rot in their mouths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23081AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23081AI\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>On that day people will be stricken by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with great panic.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23082AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23082AJ\"></sup> They will seize each other by the hand and attack one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23082AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23082AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23083AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23083AL\"></sup> too will fight at Jerusalem. The wealth of all the surrounding nations will be collected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23083AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23083AM\"></sup>—great quantities of gold and silver and clothing.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A similar plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23084AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23084AN\"></sup> will strike the horses and mules, the camels and donkeys, and all the animals in those camps.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23085AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23085AO\"></sup> from all the nations that have attacked Jerusalem will go up year after year to worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23085AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23085AP\"></sup> the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23085AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23085AQ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, and to celebrate the Festival of Tabernacles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23085AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23085AR\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If any of the peoples of the earth do not go up to Jerusalem to worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23086AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23086AS\"></sup> the King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, they will have no rain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23086AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23086AT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If the Egyptian people do not go up and take part, they will have no rain. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring on them the plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23087AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23087AU\"></sup> he inflicts on the nations that do not go up to celebrate the Festival of Tabernacles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23087AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23087AV\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This will be the punishment of Egypt and the punishment of all the nations that do not go up to celebrate the Festival of Tabernacles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23088AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23088AW\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>On that day <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">holy to the Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23089AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23089AX\"></sup> will be inscribed on the bells of the horses, and the cooking pots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23089AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23089AY\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house will be like the sacred bowls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23089AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23089AZ\"></sup> in front of the altar.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Every pot in Jerusalem and Judah will be holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23090BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23090BA\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, and all who come to sacrifice will take some of the pots and cook in them. And on that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23090BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23090BB\"></sup> there will no longer be a Canaanite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23090BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23090BC\"></sup> in the house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23090BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23090BD\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-23090BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-23090BE\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;